
DRIVER

Buttons:

A = Intake Down
B = NOTHING
X = Intake Up
Y = NOTHING

Dpad:

Down = 0 To Field
Up = Point At Hub
Left = Robot to climb position C
Right = Robot to climb position A

Bumpers:

Left = Run Outake
right = Run Intake AND Agitator

Triggers:

Left = Nothing
Right = Shoot AND Jostle

Menu Buttons:

Start = Reset Intake
Back = NOTHING
Mode = NEVER USE, sets robot to tank drive and, if pressed again, goes back to normal

Combinations: 

Left Bumper + Start = Rest Field Centric, DO NOT USE unless told to(or you know what it does)
